Project PROJECT-ASRS

    Name

        ASRS Specification

    Specification

        ASRS 1.0.0

    Document Version

        1.0.0

    Compliance Level

        Level 3


Principal HUMAN

    Type

        Human

    Description

        Software engineer writing specifications

    Can

        Read ASRS documents

        Write ASRS documents

        Modify ASRS documents


Principal AGENT

    Type

        Agent

    Description

        AI agent generating or validating ASRS

    Can

        Parse ASRS documents

        Generate ASRS documents

        Validate ASRS documents

        Convert between formats


Feature FEAT-SPECIFICATION

    Description

        ASRS language specification


Feature FEAT-TOOLS

    Description

        Tools for working with ASRS documents


Feature FEAT-EXAMPLES

    Description

        Example ASRS documents


Scenario SCN-READ-SPEC

    Principal

        HUMAN

    Given

        ASRS specification exists

    When

        Read specification

    Then

        Understand language syntax and semantics


Scenario SCN-GENERATE-ASRS

    Principal

        AGENT

    Given

        Software requirements provided

    When

        Generate ASRS document

    Then

        Valid ASRS document created


Scenario SCN-VALIDATE-ASRS

    Principal

        AGENT

    Given

        ASRS document provided

    When

        Run validator

    Then

        Validation results returned


Scenario SCN-CONVERT-FORMAT

    Principal

        AGENT

    Given

        ASRS or YAML document provided

    When

        Run converter

    Then

        Converted document produced


Component COMP-SPEC

    Type

        Library

    Description

        ASRS language specification files

    Responsibilities

        Define syntax

        Define semantics

        Define validation rules

    Verify

        MUST define all 7 entities

        MUST use RFC 2119 keywords

        MUST be unambiguous


Component COMP-VALIDATOR

    Type

        Library

    Technology

        Python

    Description

        Validates ASRS documents

    Responsibilities

        Parse ASRS syntax

        Validate entity structure

        Check reference integrity

        Report errors and warnings

    Verify

        MUST detect invalid syntax

        MUST detect duplicate IDs

        MUST detect missing required properties

        SHOULD provide line numbers in errors


Component COMP-CONVERTER

    Type

        Library

    Technology

        Python

    Description

        Converts between ASRS and YAML formats

    Responsibilities

        Parse ASRS to internal representation

        Generate YAML from internal representation

        Parse YAML to internal representation

        Generate ASRS from internal representation

    Verify

        MUST preserve all entity data

        MUST handle round-trip conversion

        MUST maintain reference integrity


Resource RES-SPEC-FILES

    Type

        Bucket

    Description

        Specification markdown files


Resource RES-EXAMPLES

    Type

        Bucket

    Description

        Example ASRS documents in YAML format


Resource RES-LOG

    Type

        Table

    Description

        Modification log for versioning

    Schema

        version_id: string

        timestamp: string

        action: string

        target: string

        block_id: string

        author: string

        description: string


Test TEST-READ-SPEC

    Validates

        SCN-READ-SPEC

        COMP-SPEC

    Given

        Spec files exist

    When

        Read specification

    Then

        Content is clear and complete


Test TEST-GENERATE-ASRS

    Validates

        SCN-GENERATE-ASRS

        COMP-CONVERTER

    Given

        Valid requirements

    When

        Generate ASRS

    Then

        Document passes validation


Test TEST-VALIDATE-ASRS

    Validates

        SCN-VALIDATE-ASRS

        COMP-VALIDATOR

    Given

        Valid ASRS document

    When

        Run validator

    Then

        No errors reported


Test TEST-CONVERT-FORMAT

    Validates

        SCN-CONVERT-FORMAT

        COMP-CONVERTER

    Given

        ASRS document

    When

        Convert to YAML and back

    Then

        Original document preserved
